    <published>2018-02-23T02:35:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-27T03:14:19.325Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-环境配置"><a href="#1-环境配置" class="headerlink" title="1. 环境配置"></a>1. 环境配置</h2><p>基于 <a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-theme-yilia</a></p><h2 id="2-百度统计"><a href="#2-百度统计" class="headerlink" title="2. 百度统计"></a>2. 百度统计</h2><ol><li>注册并登录 <a href="http://tongji.baidu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度统计</a></li><li>代码管理-代码获取-复制代码到<code>hexo/themes/yilia/_config.yml</code>中的<code>baidu_analytics</code></li></ol><h2 id="3-来必力"><a href="#3-来必力" class="headerlink" title="3. 来必力"></a>3. 来必力</h2><ol><li>注册并登录 <a href="http://laibili.com.cn/login_form" target="_blank" rel="noopener">来必力</a></li><li>安装来必力-代码管理-复制代码到<code>hexo/themes/yilia/layout/_partial/article.ejs</code></li></ol><a id="more"></a><h2 id="4-添加-RSS"><a href="#4-添加-RSS" class="headerlink" title="4. 添加 RSS"></a>4. 添加 RSS</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo/themes/yilia/_config.yml</code>配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rss: &quot;/atom.xml&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="5-添加-Sitemap"><a href="#5-添加-Sitemap" class="headerlink" title="5. 添加 Sitemap"></a>5. 添加 Sitemap</h2><h3 id="5-1-Sitemap"><a href="#5-1-Sitemap" class="headerlink" title="5.1 Sitemap"></a>5.1 Sitemap</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo/_config.yml</code>配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sitemap:</span><br><span class="line">    path: sitemap.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="5-2-baidusitemap"><a href="#5-2-baidusitemap" class="headerlink" title="5.2 baidusitemap"></a>5.2 baidusitemap</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><a href="https://ziyuan.baidu.com/linksubmit/url" target="_blank" rel="noopener">链接提交</a></li><li><a href="http://zhanzhang.baidu.com/site/siteadd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">添加网站</a><ol><li>输入网站</li><li>站点属性</li><li>验证网站，选择文件验证，下载<code>baidu_verify_KoktB8hGH2.html</code>到<code>source</code>目录下</li></ol></li></ul><p><code>hexo/_config.yml</code>配置<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">baidusitemap:</span><br><span class="line">    path: baidusitemap.xml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">skip_render:</span><br><span class="line">  - README.md</span><br><span class="line">  - baidu_verify_KoktB8hGH2.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="6-References"><a href="#6-References" class="headerlink" title="6. References"></a>6. References</h2><ul><li><a href="http://cighao.com/2016/02/14/optimization-of-hexo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo 主题优化</a></li><li><a href="http://www.arao.me/2015/hexo-next-theme-optimize-seo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">动动手指，不限于NexT主题的Hexo优化（SEO篇）</a></li><li><a href="http://www.heqiangfly.com/2016/01/11/blog-hexo-optimize/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo博客配置优化</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
